New Delhi, the 13 February, 2003
23 Magha, 1924(S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 11th February,
2003 Shri Harin Pathak assumed additional charge of the office of Minister of
State in the Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances and Pensions. He will
continue to hold the charge of the office of Minister of State in the Ministry of
Home Affairs
